column5: Tell us what NOT to do... haha
LOL I hope mine is a little longer next time out.  Cheers and thanks for the quick read this might just be the shortest post for 2010 now how many replies will it get for nothing
lol ... At least you know where fish do NOT stay.
Hey Ari did you try trolling that weedline from Cesarea to the river? that stretch is usually thick with those slimmy buggers!!

Gord, yes we did. We tried three areas that have produced for us many times, but the musky had lockjaw.  The only highlight was pulling into the marina and seeing a young lad with a walleye. The smile on his face was priceless.  Oh well, sometimes the fish have to win too.  Cheers!
